-- Ford Sees No Major Car-Market Effects From EU Crisis, HB Says
-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 2012-02-14T20:31:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-14/ford-sees-no-major-car-market-effects-from-eu-crisis-hb-says.html
Ford Motor Co. (F)  doesn’t see  Europe ’s
sovereign debt crisis affecting the region’s car market in a
significant way,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing an interview with
Alan Draper, the company’s European purchasing chief.  Ford expects the auto market in Europe to “shrink only
slightly” this year, Draper said, according to the newspaper.  Stefan Nicola in Berlin at +49-30-70010-6246 or
